dfec7a21905d3c1793e2f418286a7ef3cc","tid":283903,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T14:01:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實想自殺 都有好多種方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁食完垃圾就開心返，唔洗自殺，難道唔值得咩？<br />\n而且只係高salt姐，飲多啲水，好快柯返出來啦"},{"pid":"3d0d0ccf8bb744d8544b1c2c79bacfc861a83ded","tid":283903,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T14:02:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好似好好食咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做法好簡單，個韓國辛辣公仔麵，煮到岩岩熟就過凍水，去油益味</blockquote><br />\n健康人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n然後將罐頭啲油倒番晒落啲麵度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n罐魚啲油倒晒，們五香肉丁啲紅油一定要食，精華來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地有所不知呀"},{"pid":"deac65748b6f3f753b2604e3f96c7139d7f6150b","tid":283903,"uid":46023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T14:03:37.000Z","msg":"⑨999"},{"pid":"4881f2ec98cba7ba98b60d1826f2334055633298","tid":283903,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T14:05:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好似好好食咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做法好簡單，個韓國辛辣公仔麵，煮到岩岩熟就過凍水，去油益味</blockquote><br />\n健康人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n全post最中肯回覆<br />\n有魚有肉有菜(乾)，其實唔太差"},{"pid":"e3f73c9f0b55a425917737c217ba0d97dd855891","tid":283903,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T14:06:48.000Z","msg":"就咁煮個麵仲好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae8ee90a226e5b7eddf9d0dd730be44f3edbe45a","tid":283903,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T14:09:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就咁煮個麵仲好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n缺乏蛋白質"},{"pid":"40284f009679f78ae0c5488fb5ec78990f2614fb","tid":283903,"uid":3344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T14:11:15.000Z","msg":"正皮係俾樓豬既態度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4949ab022b779f248d8ef9ed19ebf5be81e56f18","tid":283903,"uid":81818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T14:15:38.000Z","msg":"個罐野難飲到扑街"},{"pid":"5f1931241153be46a9176ebc7bcddb503eeb81d1","tid":283903,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T14:19:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正皮係俾樓豬既態度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實，我知道的。<br />\n一開始的時候，我想開罐豆豉零魚，個扣即刻爆開左。<br />\n<br />\n佢係想講：「本是同根生，相煎何太急？」<br />\n大家都係垃圾，點解要做到咁趕盡殺絕呢？難道就不可以讓他多活一天命嗎？<br />\n<br />\n但我把心一橫，屌你老母！我俾生路你行，咁邊個俾生路我呀？<br />\n<br />\n所以我拎起支筷子狂插插插插，一ＣＭ一ＣＭ咁隊開個罐，最後一下反開佢塊皮！"},{"pid":"88125baefa147f24e9bcb31b1ef20f68ee8101d5","tid":283903,"uid":53784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T14:19:11.000Z","msg":"其實應該幾好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8707799e625d39bd68d703fbd267c2d5fe5f6f14","tid":283903,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T14:19:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實應該幾好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nit's 3am in the morning and i don't know how to say goodbye<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MuavmqfOZ6U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMuavmqfOZ6U&d=J0GRqAjvQu%2FjMp8tb0%2BH7TCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=2d11d7d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MuavmqfOZ6U</a>"},{"pid":"de8d474563e9b452da16f9306dd7cbce4c6d8d18","tid":283903,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20